Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveComedian, Debo Adebayo, on Tuesday, educated Nigerians on the role of politicians, who are in office.
He offered this insight on his Twitter handle.
He tweeted, “No politician is doing the Citizens a favour by being in office. The concept of leadership is service, selflessness and sacrifice.”
He went on to advise, “The people must unite and stop fighting themselves over politicians who only care to satisfy their own greed.”
